With solid pitching and outstanding fielding, the Phoenix A's shut down their opponents and dominated the diamond with their teamwork and determination.

stories.headline: Aurora-King Jays and Orangeville Bengals Neck and Neck in 8U Rep A Showdown!

stories.headline: Aurora-King Jays 8U A's Light Up the Scoreboard with Explosive Offense!
stories.body: The Aurora-King Jays 8U A's are dominating the 8U Rep A league with their incredible hitting skills, scoring an amazing 95 runs in just 6 games - that's an average of 15.8 runs per game! Their powerful offense has led them to a solid 4-2 record, showcasing their strength and teamwork on the field.

stories.headline: Orangeville Bengals 8U B Team Dominates with Explosive Offense!

With an impressive 4-1 record in the 8U Rep A league, these young sluggers are proving they're a force to be reckoned with!
